config SPI_GXFP3200
	tristate "Goodix GXFP3200 SPI fingerprint sensor"
	depends on SPI
	depends on ACPI || OF
	select GPIOLIB
	help
	  Say M here to build a driver skeleton for Goodix GXFP3200 SPI
	  fingerprint sensors. The driver exposes diagnostic raw SPI controls
	  through debugfs for protocol development.
